            "title": "今日我咁睇｜以伊展開談判 停火有進展 港股料試26000點 ｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/h41nyWAddmRXn0ME7tdjMQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/4a968eb3824e8e84f9556b372a56d053\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1.美伊代表談判未正式開始，而以色列攻擊黎巴嫰真主黨，令伊朗指責美國違反停火前提，不過，美國傳出已要求以色列減少對黎巴嫰真主黨的攻勢，同時以色列料與黎巴嫰談判，實際上即是與伊朗間接談判，令中東局勢有緩解的希望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2.美伊局勢附合小編之前指出邊打邊傾的局面，希望在戰場上爭取更多談判的籌碼，而以現時局面來看，美國或伊朗接受對方一開始的條件是不可能，但畢竟是大家互相開天殺價，並非代表談判無望。實際上，迫於內外壓力相信特朗普亦要宣佈勝利然後離場。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1f79787f-4a94-30d3-80b5-8228441f379c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3. 恒指估計今日在25600點至25800點有支持，有望試26000點，而下一步應該要數26200點及26500點，暫時仍有一定水位可以買入。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4.選股方面，Minimax、智譜等AI大模型股趁低吸納的策略不變，至於航空股仍是小編「油價下跌概念股」的首選，同樣值得捧場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，牛證與熊證接近一半一半的比例，屬於牛證偏低的水平，相反理論來看暫時偏向好。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E4%BB%A5%E4%BC%8A%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4-%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E6%9C%89%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E6%96%99%E8%A9%A626000%E9%BB%9E-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000503.html",
