        {
            "title": "本地｜立法會財委會下午2時開會　審議有時限柴油補貼緊急撥款申請",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"本地｜立法會財委會下午2時開會 審議有時限柴油補貼緊急撥款申請\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">本地｜<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"立法會財委會\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:立法會財委會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/立法會財委會\">立法會財委會</a>下午2時開會 審議有時限柴油補貼緊急撥款申請</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">立法會財委會今天下午2時舉行會議，將審議有關有時限柴油補貼的緊急撥款建議，預料歷時2個小時。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府公布，因應中東戰事成立「跨部門監察燃油供應專責組」，評估燃料供應及價格，確保能源供應穩定。專責組考慮到原油價格波幅影響廣泛，審慎平衡政府財政善用公帑原則後，提出4項臨時措施，包括為每公升柴油提供3元補貼，為期2個月，以支援柴油公用或商用車輛及船隻和相關工業；除私家車和電單車外所有商用車輛，使用政府收費隧道獲減費50%，為期2個月。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-467678a0-5c20-3fd9-bc0b-3491bf630fa2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">專責組又建議，設立「公共交通服務特別申請工作組」，協助公共交通營辦商應對燃油成本上升的申請；同時，動態監察局勢和油價變化，統籌政策局和部門，做好應對預案。行政長官李家超接納4項建議，指示盡快落實。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府預計，柴油價格補貼措施需要大約18億元，而減免非私家車輛的隧道費涉及少收約1.6億元費用，政府會着手與隧道費服務供應商調較收費系統以爭取盡快實施減免。相關補貼措施須經立法會財委會批准撥款。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0-%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E8%B2%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%882%E6%99%82%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83-%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%89%E6%99%82%E9%99%90%E6%9F%B4%E6%B2%B9%E8%A3%9C%E8%B2%BC%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-010001278.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 09:16:38",
